ğŸ§° rustfmt

rustfmt is a tool that formats Rust code according to the official Rust style guidelines.

Keeps your code clean, readable, and consistent across projects.

ğŸ§± cargo fmt

cargo fmt runs rustfmt on your entire project.

Automatically formats all .rs files to follow Rustâ€™s standard style rules.

Example:

cargo fmt

